replies.author: Abiral Parakash
replies.text: @Bimal Kc Bro I too can surfacely go through the problem and criticize the leader for it but that does not lead to any solution. Even in powerful country like USA leaders are linked to Russia. This is the reality of geopolitics. But where I am unsatisfied is we have given our sweat and blood to establish and institutionalise this system now I can't afford another transition and another uncertainity in the name of any issue. Our generation have grown listening these things now when we have stable government and moving towards the issue of employment and development from constitution and religion, we cannot regress back to again to the issue of monarchy and religion in any cost.
